efreshed and radiant after this treatment.</p>\n<p>Ideal for all skin types! 150$</p>\n<p>Face/neck/décolletage 250$</p>\n\";s:12:\"safe_summary\";s:0:\"\";}}}}',0,1407383157,1),('field:node:12','a:1:{s:4:\"body\";a:1:{s:3:\"und\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:5:\"value\";s:1042:\"<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Dermaplaning: </span></strong>&nbsp;is a skin resurfacing procedure that utilizes a special surgical blade to scrape away the top layer of dead epidermal cells. &nbsp;Dermaplaing&nbsp;exfoliates the skin while removing vellus hair (peach fuzz) which will NOT grow back any thicker, coarser, or blacker. It is more gentle on the skin than microdermabrasion and is ideal for sensitive skin. Dermaplaning safely refines the treated area by allowing the underlying layer of smooth, clear, undamaged skin to emerge. This procedure is most often used to improve the appearance of acne scars, small facial wrinkles and to prevent dead skin from&nbsp;building up. Dermaplaning also increases the effectiveness of skin care products to penetrate&nbsp;and make-up will&nbsp;glide on with ease for a more flawless apperance. <strong>Basic:</strong> 50$ <strong>Deluxe:</strong> 85$ <strong>Face &amp; Neck:</strong> 100$. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\";s:7:\"summary\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"format\";s:13:\"filtered_html\";s:10:\"safe_value\";s:982:\"<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Dermaplaning: </span></strong> is a skin resurfacing procedure that utilizes a special surgical blade to scrape away the top layer of dead epidermal cells.  Dermaplaing exfoliates the skin while removing vellus hair (peach fuzz) which will NOT grow back any thicker, coarser, or blacker. It is more gentle on the skin than microdermabrasion and is ideal for sensitive skin. Dermaplaning safely refines the treated area by allowing the underlying layer of smooth, clear, undamaged skin to emerge. This procedure is most often used 