INSERT INTO `field_data_body` VALUES ('node','page',0,1,1,'und',0,'<p>Marci Meixner&nbsp;Puryear&nbsp;a licensened Esthetician and Texas Tech graduate brings aesthetics and ethics together.&nbsp;Marci\'s knowledge&nbsp;of advanced skin care and Human Science background enables her&nbsp;to give each client the personal attention, respect, and information to achieve their maximum skin care goals. Dr. Michael Mendez is the on site physician at BodyScapes Medical Spa. All faciuals are preformed after an analysis and&nbsp;consultation.&nbsp; Only medical grade skin care products are used during each&nbsp;treatment including; Image Skin Care, Dr. Scwab,&nbsp; Dr. Cristine Schrammek, Obagi, and many more. Many of our medical grade products used during treatments are also available for retail.&nbsp; Now you can take the Medical Spa&nbsp;experience home with you!&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','page',0,3,3,'und',0,'<p><strong>Acne Facial: Includes deep pore cleansing utilizing steam and specifice medical grade acne products.&nbsp; All acne facials include an&nbsp;enzyme mask to target bacteria and congested pores, extractions, exfoliation, restorative mask and serums specifically to treat acne.&nbsp;Face 60$ Face &amp; Neck 75&amp;&nbsp;&nbsp; *Add Blue light therapy for 20$</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Image IPeel Treatments for Acne: </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Acne&nbsp;Peel:&nbsp;(oily,&nbsp;acne, impure skin) Potent blend of alpha and beta hydroxy acids with anti-inflammatory agents to treat and heal acne lesions.&nbsp; Botanical lighteners help fade acne scarring. For Optimal results 6 treatments at 2 week intervals.&nbsp;100$/each or 550$/pkg of 6&nbsp;(50$ savings).</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Beta Peel:&nbsp; (Acne grades III-IV, oily, acne prone, aging) Powerful non-bleneded hydroxy acid treatment targets and improves moderate to severe breakouts.&nbsp; Provides smoother skin and reduction of acne within 24hrs.&nbsp; For Optimal results&nbsp;4 treatments at 2 week intervals.&nbsp;150$/each or 550$/pkg of&nbsp;4&nbsp;(50$ savings).&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>*Blue Light Therapy:</strong> prevents and even reverses mild to moderate cases of acne without the use of harsh chemicals. Blue light wavelengths target the bacteria without harming the surface of the skin. This procedure heals acne blemishes and prevents future outbreaks. From teens to adults, it\'s a simple way to take control of acne and promote a clearer and more beautiful complexion.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','page',0,4,4,'und',0,'<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Teen Facial:&nbsp;</span> Get your teen started on the right track with a&nbsp;gentle refreshing&nbsp;facial and help prevent breakouts.&nbsp;&nbsp;Your teen will experience steam accompanied with gentle cleansers, exfoliants, extractions only if necessay, mask and serums customized for their delicate skin, moisturizer, and SPF protection. 50$ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','page',0,6,6,'und',0,'<p>Signature facial: Skin is cleansed and examined to customize a specific facial for your skin. Includes extractions, exfoliation, customized serums, masks, and creams to maximize your skins potential. Hand and neck massage with aroma therapy.</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','page',0,7,7,'und',0,'<p>European Facial info</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','page',0,8,8,'und',0,'<p>Microdermabrasion: Crystal and Diamond treatments available. Microdermabrasion provides deep exfoliation and resurfacing. This treatment is noninvasive and removes a few top layers of the skin called the stratum corneum. This treatment will improve the appearance of wrinkles, hyperpigmentation(sun spots), scarring, enlarged pores, and acne.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Face: 80$</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Face/neck: 100$</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Face/neck/décolletage: 150$</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Back: 250$</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hands: 30$</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Arms: 60$</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','page',0,9,9,'und',0,'<p>Oxygen Facials</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','page',0,10,10,'und',0,'<p>Chemical peels are only&nbsp;performed after a skin care evaluation to ensure our clients are candidates for a&nbsp;treatment plan or&nbsp;individual procedure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Herbal Green Peel:</strong></span>&nbsp; (All skin types) 100$</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Ormedic Lift:</strong> (Unbalanced skin, sensitive,&nbsp;pregnant, teens, menopause) </span>&nbsp;Non-chemical peel with organic blends such as papaya, pineapple, and mango that naturally balance, regenerate, and restore skin for a healthy fresh glow. For Optimal results 6 treatments at 2 week intervals.&nbsp;125$/each or 700$/pkg of 6&nbsp;(50$ savings).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\">O2 Lift:&nbsp; </span></strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\">(All Skin Types)</span>&nbsp;Luxurious treatment infuses oxygen, plant-derived stem cells, peptides and a high concentration of enzymatic botanicals into the skin leaving it luminous and dewy. 150$</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Signature Facelift:&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>(Dry/dehydrated rosacea sensitive) Result-driven treatment with vitamin C, alpha and beta hydroxy&nbsp;acids and&nbsp;gentle&nbsp;yet effective enzymes speed up cellular turnover. Treatment&nbsp;lightens, tightens, and brightens. For Optimal results&nbsp;6 treatments&nbsp;at 2 week intervals. 150$/each or 850$/pkg of 6(50$ savings).</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Lightening Lift/Peel:</strong>&nbsp; (pigmentation, redness,&nbsp;sun spots, photo damage) Highly effective treatment blends lactic acid and Kojic acid to reduce pigmentation, redness&nbsp;and works to&nbsp;correct uneven skin tones.&nbsp; For Optimal results 6 treatments at 2 week intervals.&nbsp;100$/each or 550$/pkg of 6&nbsp;(50$ savings).</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Wrinkle Lift/Peel:</strong>&nbsp; (aging, fine lines/wrinkles, rough skin, photo aging) Ultra resurfacing blend of glycolic acid and retinol&nbsp;visibly reduces the appearance&nbsp;of fine lines and wrinkles, leaving skin firm and revitalized.&nbsp;&nbsp;For Optimal results 6 treatments at 2 week intervals.&nbsp;150$/each or 850$/pkg of 6&nbsp;(50$ savings).&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>Perfection Peel:</strong>&nbsp; (advanced aging and&nbsp;pigmentation) Resurfacing treatment uses next generation blends of advanced exfoliating and revitalizing ingredients.&nbsp;&nbsp;Exclusive blend of hydroxy acid treatment, retinol, stem cells and peptides to create \"perfection.\"&nbsp; For Optimal results 6 treatments at 2 week intervals.&nbsp;175$ </span><span style=\"font-size:14px\">&nbsp;(possible 5-6 days of downtime&nbsp;w/o sun exposure&nbsp;due to peeling and flaking) </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>TCA Orange Peel:</strong> (advanced aging, severe sun-damaged, acne scarring) TCA/salicylic/retinol blend that aggressively treats aging, sun damaged skin, and acne scarring. One application reveals a new you!&nbsp;1-2 treatments recommended per year. 200$ must purchase after care essentials.&nbsp;(substantial amount of peeling and flaking&nbsp;6-7 days downtime w/o sun exposure)&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n','','filtered_html'),('node','page',0,11,11,'und',0,'<p>Hydrafacial:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This revolutionary medical treatment combines deep pore cleansing, exfoliation, extractions, antioxidants and hyluaronic acid (binds 1000x it\'s weight in water).&nbsp; Vortex technology customized tips deliver medical grade serums to each pore for the maximum facial! The Hydrafacial utilizes specially created vitamin enriched serums that are infused into the s